Hilo Hattie https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hilo_Hattie 0 Hilo Hattie (born Clarissa Haili, October 28, 1901 – December 12, 1979) was a Hawaiian singer, hula dancer, actress and comedian of Native Hawaiian ancestry.
